RACE.RACE_TEXT: Prairie Dash S. PRAIRIE MEADOWS RACE 3 300 Y Dirt CR: 91. Stakes Purse 25000. FOR THREE-YEAR-OLDS AND UPWARD. No Nomination Fee. $100.00 to pass the entry box with an additional $200.00 to start. $25,000 guaranteed of which 50% to the winner, 17% to second, 10% to third, 6% to fourth, 5% to fifth, 3% to sixth and seventh and 2% to eighth through tenth finishers. Trainer entries will be limited to no more than five (5) in this race. Starters to be named through the entry box at the usual time of closing. Limited to ten (10 ) starters.
